column5: IM OUTTA HERE SEE YA ALL NEXT WEEK
See you on Friday...around the dinner hour!
I'll be pulling in around midnight tomorrow....the honking and Jeep spots on your tent flap will be moi.
I'll be there around noon tomorrow, maybe a little earlier.  Prolly still be sober around midnight Roy...I thought you were a leg man!
They will be cold and waiting for you Roy.   May have to wait till Friday a.m. to meet the little guy though.
